Package: AltrepPointer
Type: Package
Title: A Wrapper for C++ Vector Pointers
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-07-01
Author: Jiefei Wang
Maintainer: Jiefei Wang <szwjf08@gmail.com>
Description: The package uses ALTREP API to wrap a vector pointer. 
  The wrapper behaves the same as a regular R vector.
  Users can directly manipulate the pointer without the need of calling C++ function.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.6.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
